{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/About.gif?t=1676515242\" /><br>The Specter Chronicles is a cyberpunk visual novel that combines text-based adventure with turn-based tactical combat.<br><br>You are a Specter, a highly-trained enforcer of the Warden who rules over humanity as a godlike algorithmic entity. You have suffered a severe memory loss during a mission to track down the Prophet, a rebel leader who defies the Warden\u2019s regime. With the help of a neural engineer, you must restore your memories by reliving them.<br><br>But what will you discover in your own memories?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore a dystopian world through branching narratives driven by your decisions</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/BranchingNarrative.gif?t=1676515242\" /><br>Are you a brute who decimates everyone and everything that stands in your path? Or are you a smooth operator who prefers to avoid confrontation? The decision is yours.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defeat your opponents using a unique combat system</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/UniqueCombatSystem.gif?t=1676515242\" /><br>Engage in turn-based combat where you can combine 6 basic attacks into combos, counters, and feints.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tailor your gear to suit your fighting style</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/TailorYourGear.gif?t=1676515242\" /><br>Install mods into your weapon and armor to infuse unique properties and functions, such as adding bonus points to an attribute or granting a buff during combat.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Randomized runs</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/RandomizedRuns.gif?t=1676515242\" /><br>The fragments of memories that you encounter during a run will be randomly drawn, allowing you to revisit the memories that you want and discard the ones that you don\u2019t.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This game is for you if you\u2026</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy text-based adventures that read like novellas.<br></li><li>Are looking for a break from card battlers and typical RPG combat - the combat system in The Specter Chronicles is definitely one-of-a-kind!<br></li><li>Are a comic book fan.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This game is NOT for you if you\u2026</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Don\u2019t like text-heavy games.<br></li><li>Prefer action-based combat over turn-based combat.</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2243880?t=1676515242","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1676515242","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1676515242","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1676515242","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"This Game may contain content not appropriate for all ages, or may not be appropriate for viewing at work: Comic Book Violence, Fictional Drug Use"},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/About.gif?t=1676515242\" /><br>The Specter Chronicles is a cyberpunk visual novel that combines text-based adventure with turn-based tactical combat.<br><br>You are a Specter, a highly-trained enforcer of the Warden who rules over humanity as a godlike algorithmic entity. You have suffered a severe memory loss during a mission to track down the Prophet, a rebel leader who defies the Warden\u2019s regime. With the help of a neural eng